@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cemcpa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.abs(v1 + 0.40) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.45)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(0.12) / wp.exp((v2 + 0.78 - tmp + 0.92)))
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.56 * v0 + 0.65)) * (wp.sin(v2 + 0.06) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.98)))
    v0 = (tmp - v1)
    tmp = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.66 / tmp + 0.23) * (v1 + 0.84 / v1 + 0.91)))
    v0 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.54 / v0 + 0.59) - 0.60))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v1 + 0.33) / (tmp + 0.24 * v1 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
